{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2857380/extras/SYWTV.png?t=1731250188\" /><br><strong>Destroy as many tentacles as you can, gather enough flesh to strengthen your Ooze, and annihilate the mighty Ancient Gods.</strong><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2857380/extras/separateur.gif?t=1731250188\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2857380/extras/GAMEPLAY.png?t=1731250188\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Prepare your game and aim for the highest score.</h2>Accumulate perseverance points by defeating the Ancient God! Spend them at the beginning of the game to increase the difficulty and achieve a better score. <br>Will you rise to the top of the leaderboard?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2857380/extras/ScreenStart.png?t=1731250188\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Control your sanity!</h2>The world is hostile, and madness looms over you. Your sanity is impacted by the mere presence of your enemies, their counterattacks, and the passage of time. It's up to you to regain your balance by eliminating the creeping threat.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2857380/extras/insanity.gif?t=1731250188\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Be cautious of your life!</h2>Movement comes at a cost; study the terrain carefully and move wisely. Some prefer to charge headfirst and lay the foundations for their successors...<br>The choice is yours.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2857380/extras/23042.gif?t=1731250188\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Sacrifice yourself at the right moment!</h2>Your Ooze is weak. Sacrifice it before its death to strengthen the power of the next one. But beware, you have on